al spin that is a $p^n$-th root of unity for some $n$. It also leads\nto a simple demonstration that all Abelian topological phases can be\nrepresented by $U(1)^N$ Chern-Simons theory parameterized by a K-matrix.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2013 20:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2013 18:45:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2014 15:58:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-28"}
