rm of this conjecture also allows auxiliary\nvariables, as discussed in depth in the Outlook.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2013 22:20:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2013 04:56:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-11"}
