fication of the latter\noscillations as $m$=0 modes plausible. The identification of $m$=1 g-modes is\nless straightforward, while many of the unstable even $m$=2 g-modes may\ncorrespond to observed weaker photometric variations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Oct 2013 10:03:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
